{"tid":1822033,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"(外國戰線,抵制不道德的消費)呼籲外國人抵制中国制產品和中国品牌","createTime":"2020-01-12T16:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T04:57:12.000Z","uid":76310,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bfb9f92747b7f95c5d38651000d808a4c533464a","tid":1822033,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T16:39:02.000Z","msg":"呼籲外國人抵制中国制產品和中国品牌<br />\n<br />\n外國, 曾經發起抵制破壞環境既產品/公司, 也試過抵制使用童工的公司/產品<br />\n成功過或者有一定成效<br />\n其實很多鬼佬公司或產品, 要求唔可以使用童工或者破壞環境之類<br />\n所以抵制不道德的消費, 呼籲外國人抵制中国制產品和中国品牌是絕對合理和可行的<br />\n<br />\n為什麼使用中国制產品和中国品牌是不道德?<br />\n1. 新疆集中營, 干犯人道罪行<br />\n2. 西藏鎮壓, 干犯人道罪行<br />\n3. 香港警暴, 干犯人道罪行<br />\n4. 將言論審查伸展到世界各國, 違反普世價值<br />\n5. 將貪污行賄腐敗推廣到世界各國, 違反普世價值<br />\n6. 將獨裁政治推廣到世界各國, 違反普世價值"},{"pid":"5cef0395f58e32fa3f787f6964f425bdbd0964e2","tid":1822033,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T16:40:09.000Z","msg":"具體又點做, 如何推廣, 大家有沒有什麼意見?<br />\n呢樣野, 要發大來做, 一來可以經濟切斷中共財路, 二來可以宣揚強国衰野, 三來等同外國文宣"},{"pid":"28b0eab40459322d5c4d0198e2cdb053141435c5","tid":1822033,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T16:41:37.000Z","msg":"大家覺得可以點做?<br />\n將以上六點, 總結, 再以某名義寄去各歐美大型零售商, 要求抵制強国?"},{"pid":"b36bf070bc54ecde8092133dcfacfa1c246dff67","tid":1822033,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T16:46:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d78ffc42d1b57a4e272a58b6384ee2e01b15f96","tid":1822033,"uid":143260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T16:48:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3c45f050b517fae1f7d107f4d6cf6816b7856317","tid":1822033,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T16:58:07.000Z","msg":"1. 新疆集中營, 干犯人道罪行<br />\n2. 西藏鎮壓, 干犯人道罪行<br />\n3. 香港警暴, 干犯人道罪行<br />\n4. 將言論審查伸展到世界各國, 違反普世價值<br />\n5. 將貪污行賄腐敗推廣到世界各國, 違反普世價值<br />\n6. 將獨裁政治推廣到世界各國, 違反普世價值<br />\n<br />\n將這6點集合和總結成一份資料和報告, 寄過去外國零售公司, 批發商, 大型百貨公司, 要求他們抵制中国制產品和中国品牌"},{"pid":"0922025b84deacf9d14ce41653ed074c7adf8428","tid":1822033,"uid":256309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T17:02:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"59aa86ca95ee1a56fe21cd2fc8ecc19ec0b4fb3f","tid":1822033,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T17:08:00.000Z","msg":"實際行動要推<br />\n<br />\nTwitter / Facebook #ABC_challenge #boycottChina<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n警暴製亂<br />\n支暴製亂</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0Ezf7k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0Ezf7k.jpg&h=0e61caff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n狗隊特突比你捉到鬼，反正比你捉到隻鬼又唔會有咩後果，仲可以引大家捉鬼，透過捉鬼內部分化<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n沒有普選 唯有獨立</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ytpdxK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ytpdxK.jpg&h=cebe6b32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">荷包在我手 藍店抖一抖</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">抵制藍店 支持黃色經濟圈</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u603t5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu603t5D.jpg&h=0f9c2c73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府正用盡一切手段迫企業歸邊，為示威者樹敵，為求社會各界與抗爭人士割蓆<br />\n<br />\n黑警透過非法濫捕，圖阻嚇港人表達訴求，損害香港言論、集會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">解散警隊 刻不容緩</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2P6wEt9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2P6wEt9.jpg&h=75dfc14f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ec3npyj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fec3npyj.jpg&h=648ef6a